        }
      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A 45-year-old patient is scheduled for coagulation studies to assess their clotting function. To prevent blood clotting during the tests, which of the following anticoagulants is commonly used in coagulation studies?</span></span></span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q7203739",
      "question_audio": null,
      "question_video": null,
      "map_id": 32000,
