      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A laboratory technician is preparing blood samples for various tests requiring the chelation of calcium ions to prevent blood clotting. Which of the following anticoagulants is commonly used?</span></span></span></p>",
